      "username": "Z0NK0UT",
      "name": "Chad @ LZX Industries",
      "created_at": "2020-02-22T16:54:12.878Z",
      "updated_at": "2020-02-22T16:54:12.878Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Sorry to hear the Vidiot is giving you trouble. Have you checked the PAL/NTSC switch to make sure you are in the correct format? Have you tried changing the sync loop-through setting on the back? Sometimes it helps to power cycle Vidiot after changing those settings.</p>",
